   133	## 5. SUCCESS CRITERIA
   134	
   135	- **SC-001**: Every references and assets file lives under a lane subdir and the skill loads with no broken path literal.
   136	- **SC-002**: Grep for the old function-dir and flat-asset literals in SKILL.md returns nothing.
   137	<!-- /ANCHOR:success-criteria -->
