   143	
   144	| Type | Item | Impact | Mitigation |
   145	|------|------|--------|------------|
   146	| Risk | Missed path literal in SKILL.md | Med | grep sweep both old patterns after the edit, expect zero hits |
   147	| Risk | Lane misclassification of a doc | Low | follow the recorded mapping, shared holds only loop and promotion docs both lanes use |
