.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/004-fix-hardening-review-findings-for-benchmark-mode/spec.md:75:The 122 deep review confirmed (post Opus-4.8 arbitration) 3 unique P1 correctness/security defects in the shipped model-benchmark mode — the dispatcher drops the requested working directory for 4 of 5 executors, the D3 path guard misclassifies sibling-prefix paths, acceptance criteria run un-gated shell commands, and the D4 grader accepts unbounded model scores — plus 11 P2 advisories. None is P0, but the P1s warrant fix-before-promote.
