.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/decision-record.md:2:title: "Decision Record: deep-agent-improvement model-benchmark mode"
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/decision-record.md:3:description: "Architecture decisions for adding a model/prompt-framework benchmark mode to deep-agent-improvement: mode selector, pluggable seams, reuse map."
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/decision-record.md:7:  - "deep-agent-improvement seams"
