.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/spec.md:2:title: "Feature Specification: deep-agent-improvement model-benchmark mode (design)"
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/spec.md:3:description: "Design to add a model/prompt-framework benchmark mode to deep-agent-improvement via a mode selector, porting the 120/003 rig behind pluggable candidate/dispatcher/scorer seams. Design only; no implementation in this packet."
