.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/003-build-benchmark-mode/spec.md:59:This is **Phase 3** of packet 121 (add a model-benchmark mode to deep-agent-improvement). It executes the build-delta produced by phase 002's MiniMax M2.7 deep research (canonical source: `../002-implementation-deep-research/research/research.md`, §10 Build-delta). Phase 001 holds the architecture ADRs; this phase implements them.
