deep-research/research/.deep-research.lock\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/004-validation-and-docs/graph-metadata.json\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/003-skill-benchmark-mode/graph-metadata.json\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/002-skill-rename-deep-improvement/graph-metadata.json\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/graph-metadata.json\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/graph-metadata.json\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/004-validation-and-docs/description.json\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/003-skill-benchmark-mode/description.json\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/002-skill-rename-deep-improvement/description.json\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-